attributes.mlflow.spanInputs:
{"database_schema": ""Description for table: DexAmmProtocol"
type DexAmmProtocol implements Protocol @entity @regularPolling {
  "Unique identifier for the protocol"
  id: ID!
  "Name of the decentralized exchange protocol"
  name: String!
  "URL-friendly version of the protocol name"
  slug: String!
  "Version of the schema used by the protocol"
  schemaVersion: String!
  "Version of the subgraph for the protocol"
  subgraphVersion: String!
  "Version of the methodology applied"
  methodologyVersion: String!
  "Blockchain network where the protocol operates"
  network: Network!
  "Type of protocol, e.g., AMM"
  type: ProtocolType!
  "Total value locked in USD within the protocol"
  totalValueLockedUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Value controlled by the protocol in USD"
  protocolControlledValueUSD: BigDecimal
  "Cumulative trading volume in USD"
  cumulativeVolumeUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative revenue generated for liquidity providers in USD"
  cumulativeSupplySideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative revenue generated for the protocol in USD"
  cumulativeProtocolSideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Total cumulative revenue in USD"
  cumulativeTotalRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Total number of unique users interacting with the protocol"
  cumulativeUniqueUsers: Int!
  "Total number of liquidity pools within the protocol"
  totalPoolCount: Int!
  "Daily snapshots of usage metrics"
  dailyUsageMetrics: [UsageMetricsDailySnapshot!]! @derivedFrom(field: "protocol")
  "Hourly snapshots of usage metrics"
  hourlyUsageMetrics: [UsageMetricsHourlySnapshot!]! @derivedFrom(field: "protocol")
  "Daily snapshots of financial metrics"
  financialMetrics: [FinancialsDailySnapshot!]! @derivedFrom(field: "protocol")
  "List of liquidity pools associated with the protocol"
  pools: [LiquidityPool!]! @derivedFrom(field: "protocol")
  "List of pool identifiers"
  _poolIDs: [ID!]!
  "Default trading fee rate applied by the protocol"
  _defaultTradingFeeRate: BigDecimal!
  "Fee rate applied by the network"
  _networkFeeRate: BigDecimal!
  "Fee rate applied on withdrawals"
  _withdrawalFeeRate: BigDecimal!
}"}
